<div class="read-page">
  <p class="section-label">本書</p>
  <h1>多元宇宙：協作技術與民主的未來</h1>
  <p class="read-page__intro">
    按章節瀏覽。本書由全球志願者社群翻譯為多種語言。
  </p>

  <p class="read-page__lang-note">
    <a href="/read/">Read in English &rarr;</a>
  </p>

  <div class="chapter-groups">
    {% for section in chapters.sections %}
      <div class="chapter-group reveal">
        <h3 class="chapter-group__title">
          <span class="chapter-group__accent" style="background:{{ section.color }}"></span>
          {{ i18n.zh.sections[section.title] or section.title }}
        </h3>
        <div class="chapter-list">
          {% for ch in section.chapters %}
            {% set zhData = translations.zh.files[ch.id] %}
            {% if zhData %}
              <a href="/zh/read/{{ ch.id }}/" class="chapter-card reveal" style="border-top-color:{{ section.color }}">
                <span class="chapter-card__number">{{ ch.number }}</span>
                <span class="chapter-card__title">{{ zhData.title }}</span>
              </a>
            {% endif %}
          {% endfor %}
        </div>
      </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</div>
